The Manager of Inventory Acquisition plays a critical role to the success of ScoreBig.&nbsp; In this role you will need to become an expert on the secondary ticket market.&nbsp; You will be responsible for working with current partners and prospects in order to secure margin bearing ticket inventory.&nbsp; You will need to understand our partner&rsquo;s goals, pain points and needs in order to help drive incremental revenue while mitigating losses on inventory that would otherwise go unsold.</p>
